money markets are operational in Mumbai) then the payment shall be made on the
succeeding Business Day (as per the original repayment schedule) without payment
of interest for such additional period.
n case if the principal redemption dale falls on a day which is not a Business Day
Business Day being a day excluding Saturdays, Sundays on which money

in relation to any date on which a payment has to be made by the Issuer in

ind the trustee, IDBl Trusteeship Services Ltd.
